class=\"g-hp-election-reporter-text s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\">Kamala Harris is shattering precedents, but it is easier to see her as president in light of her story as a daughter of motivated immigrants and as a longtime prosecutor. She favors facts over ideology. Her guardedness, as an often prejudged woman of color, makes her aware of inequities in policy. </div></div> <div class=\"g-hp-desktop-border s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"></div> <div class=\"g-hp-election-story Comes After a Series of Career Risks</div> </div></div> </a></div> </div></div> </div><div class=\"g-carousel-item even\"><div class=\"g-candidate-card\"><div class=\"g-hp-election-module regulations. If elected again, he would kill any federal effort to study and fight climate change, encourage oil and gas companies to \u201cDrill, Baby, Drill\u201d and restrict the government agency that protects air and water. </div></div> <div class=\"g-hp-desktop-border s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"></div> <div class=\"g-hp-election-story s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><a Choice: Trump vs. Harris on Climate Change</div> </div></div> </a></div> </div></div> </div><div class=\"g-carousel-item odd\"><div class=\"g-candidate-card\"><div class=\"g-hp-election-module </div></a> <div class=\"g-hp-desktop-border s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"></div> <div class=\"g-hp-election-reporter s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><div class=\"g-hp-election-reporter-byline s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><img suppress protests he deems riots, patrol Democratic-run cities he deems crime dens and hunt for undocumented immigrants. The strongman tactics would carry profound implications for individual rights and constraints on federal power. </div></div> <div class=\"g-hp-desktop-border s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"></div> <div class=\"g-hp-election-reporter-text s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\">Donald Trump wants to cut taxes in novel and potentially very expensive ways if he returns to the White House. He would instead impose broad tariffs on imports to fund the government. Taken together, his plans could remake the nation\u2019s tax system, placing a greater burden on low-income Americans.\n </div></div> <div class=\"g-hp-desktop-border s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"></div> <div class=\"g-hp-election-story s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2024/10/17/us/politics/trump-tax-cuts.html\" class=\"s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><div class=\"g-hp-election-story-link s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><b class=\"g-hp-election-story-label s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\">Read the story</b> <div class=\"inner s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><div class=\"g-hp-election-story-thumb s-hHr7kJNQYH7n\"><img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2024/10/16/multimedia/DC-TRUMP-TAX-01-tmwv/DC-TRUMP-TAX-01-tmwv-smallSquare252.jpg\"></div> <div class=\"g-hp-election-story-promo\">Trump Promises New Tax Cuts. Wade, allowing states to ban abortion. He has said he would not sign a national ban if Congress passed one.
